{"tid":2036033,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"何氏家族宣布何鴻燊死訊","createTime":"2020-05-26T08:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T14:14:48.000Z","uid":214218,"like":5,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"40de7a095965e94c50752317c004be395a658703","tid":2036033,"uid":214218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cRM9EL2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRM9EL2.jpg&h=b6e23760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們何鴻燊的家族懷着極沉痛的心情向大家宣布，今日爸爸終於在剛才一點鐘，在香港養和醫院安詳離世，享年98歲。何博士多年來在香港是舉足輕重，德高望重，好愛惜香港人，亦都傳承了一些對我們家庭的教育來講，好重要的人生教誨，取之社會，用之社會，一向以來都是他重要的原則，我們將會繼績秉承。雖然我們知道這天終會來臨，但是亦無減我們今日難以言喻的悲傷。何博士，我爸爸會永遠留在我們所有家人的心中，我們希望以自己的上進心繼續去完成我爸爸一直以來希望做到的，惠澤於社會的一些責任。我們已經有共識集體共同去處理爸爸的後事。<br />\n<br />\n捱到98歲都算係咁，呢幾年有種活死人嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要有時比啲仔女Post IG FB當公仔咁玩<br />\n <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZAkXIa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZAkXIa&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=9b7fd9ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZAkXIa</a>"},{"pid":"95a2b177bd5590fe498b1bbe9a5d0bc8f01075fb","tid":2036033,"uid":30006,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"巴打今日工作好忙？"},{"pid":"db2319b80a4a7ba5c3b8018eae3b0f233d640b51","tid":2036033,"uid":137627,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"點解會自己讚親人舉足輕重，德高望重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4a7a3720e5d5846c759d2dd5a4b4e9ee556d5d","tid":2036033,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"very good"},{"pid":"35173e4893f6448ce56b22803ef25e4268f2db8f","tid":2036033,"uid":2772,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"咩事死老豆咁既閪樣"},{"pid":"66e328c74dcf8522d436db33a1edfa1e108bac0b","tid":2036033,"uid":66805