nail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRM9EL2.jpg&h=b6e23760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們何鴻燊的家族懷着極沉痛的心情向大家宣布，今日爸爸終於在剛才一點鐘，在香港養和醫院安詳離世，享年98歲。何博士多年來在香港是舉足輕重，德高望重，好愛惜香港人，亦都傳承了一些對我們家庭的教育來講，好重要的人生教誨，取之社會，用之社會，一向以來都是他重要的原則，我們將會繼績秉承。雖然我們知道這天終會來臨，但是亦無減我們今日難以言喻的悲傷。何博士，我爸爸會永遠留在我們所有家人的心中，我們希望以自己的上進心繼續去完成我爸爸一直以來希望做到的，惠澤於社會的一些責任。我們已經有共識集體共同去處理爸爸的後事。<br />\n<br />\n捱到98歲都算係咁，呢幾年有種活死人嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要有時比啲仔女Post IG FB當公仔咁玩<br />\n <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZAkXIa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZAkXIa&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=9b7fd9ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZAkXIa</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:12:46.000Z","msg":"見到我們何鴻燊的家族就唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜鳩中文嚟"},{"pid":"bfa95c1741d719e21dbb0d0ea0a536e92a2aa88b","tid":2036033,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"零件停產，進入digital年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ca9caf3f2ff9b5a505b2f377ea48fee07b8f3a","tid":2036033,"uid":76314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee08531f4ad7cab4092226769abf6e200b624baf","tid":2036033,"uid":83912,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"015ee5870afabeb0815988609b7a372e3e4bfa5b","tid":2036033,"uid":76314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:50:56.000Z","msg":"無一個人嗰樣係喊過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"佢地應該慶祝開香檳都黎唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇佢地早排狂結婚生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其四太啲仔女，同親都係蝗<br />\n應該會拿拿聲分錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:15:04.000